source.name: SFO Passenger, Cargo, Aircraft Landing Datasets
source.description: The SFO air traffic datasets include passenger counts, cargo weight, and aircraft landing counts and landed weight at the airport. Data is updated quarterly, and in addition to the CSV format, there are sample Excel spreadsheets pre-populated with the data and with several pivot tables created as an example of how the data can be used. Data analysis tips are included on the dataset webpage.
